channel.title: Mass music upload this month
channel.description:
I'm going to be uploading 62 of the music tracks I've made since August to my YouTube channel sometime next week as I spend this week rendering all of the videos. I will not, however, be uploading them to my SoundCloud as I have completely run out of upload time.
Hoping at least someone might find some interest in this, and look forward to the upload. I'll share all the tracks here as a playlist on the day I upload them.

item.title: Mass music upload this month
item.dc:creator: Nindota
item.description:
I’m currently planning on uploading the tracks Monday, and making them public on Tuesday, though depending on a few different factors, that may be pushed back to Wednesday.
Additionally, seeing as most people will likely not have the time to listen to all 62 tracks, I’ll be putting together smaller playlist of what I believe to be the 10 best of the 62 tracks.

Anyways, as before, hoping at least someone might find some interest in this, and look forward to it.
